data.description: What a beautiful home located in Chestnut Hills Neighborhood in Pike Township. This home offers elegance, pride in ownership and a soaring 2 story entry.  You'll love the warm colors, fresh paint and new flooring throughout.  The 2 story Living Room leads to the dining area with tall windows.  The Family Room has a Fireplace, Eat in Kitchen has stainless appliances and planning desk.  Both rooms lead to a huge Sunroom which is a great bonus for this home.  The attractive staircase leads to the upper level with 3 bedrooms which includes a spacious Owner's Suite with a spa like bathroom with dual vanities, garden tub and separate shower.  Home is located on a cul-de-sac street, has easy access to highways 465 and 65 and is located near Eagle Creek Park.
